rComments: I really enjoyed this course. I was worried about taking stats since AP Stats was difficult for me, but he made the material easy and my TA was great. Bought the textbook but never opened it. He was a very nice person and I highly recommend this course. Hoping to take more with him!!!

Audun is everything I wish the US educational system was. He's the one prof I've ever had who truly encourages questions, loves feedback, connects with the students, and actually communicates the information perfectly. He emphasizes understanding concepts & really *learning* the material. He is absolutely the best prof I have ever had, hands down.

Professor Dahl was by far one of the top 3 teachers I've had in MY LIFE. The man is enthusiastic, clear, and teaches with a purpose. It's clear that he is passionate about his subject and encourages students to ask questions and participate. I would definitely recommend him if you need to fulfill your SR GE

Audun is extremely funny and makes the lectures worth going to. He posts the lecture slides online however, so if you don't go its no big deal. There's a lot of extra credit opportunities (tests are 120/100 etc). The course material is pretty easy, especially if you've taken AP Stats before, as I did. Overall I loved him.
Professor Dahl is a sweetheart - truly cares about student success. And he give you the statistics formulas on the tests.
